name: Chaos Orb Warehouse Crawler #DCJam2023
description:
Made for https://itch.io/jam/dcjam2023

It's all about the orbs.  Stare into the orbs.  Get to the exit I guess. But don't forget to look into the orbs.

Volume settings are available in the panel at the top for sfx and the little song playing I made with beepbox.co.

There are three levels that can be selected in the settings panel at the top. Comment your high scores!
